{"tid":629722,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"被毛舜筠演技震撼視為勁敵 Stephy爭影后：未識得緊張","createTime":"2018-04-15T03:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T08:46:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"51d969da0274d7b67b579fd18aaafa8edd7639d6","tid":629722,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180415/20361753?_ga=2.11242420.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361753%3F_ga%3D2.11242420.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=87729510\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F20361753%3F_ga%3D2.11242420.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=727a9265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180415/20361753?_ga=2.11242420.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n被毛舜筠演技震撼視為勁敵<br />\nStephy爭影后：未識得緊張<br />\n<br />\n2.8K<br />\n娛樂名人<br />\n<br />\n【第37屆香港電影金像獎之影帝影后篇】鄧麗欣（Stephy）及周秀娜以80後身份，今晚在尖沙嘴文化中心爭奪香港電影金像獎最佳女主角。Stephy在《空手道》的表現，被指煥然一新，早前已先為她贏得電影評論學會最佳女演員，理所當然成為賽前大熱，她認為緣份到自然會贏。影后最大對手是《黃金花》的毛舜筠，她曾兩度入圍女主角、擁有40多年演藝經驗，難怪Stephy看好毛姐。<br />\n<br />\n現年34歲的鄧麗欣首次以最佳女主角身份候選人現身，踏足金像獎紅地毯。她在《空手道》的演出有目共睹，電影評論學會早前亦為她加持，頒發最佳女演員獎，被看好成為奪獎大熱門。早前她接受訪問，談到大熱時，笑言：「其實我唔係好知大唔大熱呢樣嘢，到𠵱家都未識去面對呢個心情。<br />\n<br />\n好多人問我『會唔會緊張呀？或者有壓力』，其實我未識得有壓力，未識得緊張。」她指評論學會的獎項，已令她有種有着落的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStephy認為在對的時間遇到《空手道》平川真理一角，是好大的緣份。攝影：陳俊強<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在《空手道》的表現煥然一新的Stephy，成功擺脫花瓶形象。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p5e.jpg&h=3e12734d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStephy曾參與拍過不少愛情片，她覺得將來有可能會繼續拍。《失戀日》劇照<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會拍愛情片<br />\n<br />\n談到拍《空》片及贏獎，Stephy說：「所有獎項或者入圍出現，其實都係一個好大嘅緣份，無論遇到呢部戲或者遇到大家，其實係一個好啱嘅時間，可能幾年前我遇到平川真理呢個角色，未必有今日嘅效果。大家覺得我拍好多愛情片，我覺得將來都可能會繼續拍愛情片，只不過將來嘅我演愛情片，同以前嘅我演愛情片，其實已經係唔一樣嘅我。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前獲評論學會頒最佳女演員的Stephy，自言感到有着落。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/1523709764_4194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F1523709764_4194.jpg&h=72d57214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStephy為拍攝《空手道》，下過不少苦功。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「覺得佢搞笑」<br />\n<br />\nStephy直言有看過所有對手的戲，對毛姐印象最深：「因為我心目中都仲係會覺得佢係搞笑，同埋成日都會記住佢喺《家有囍事》裏面嗰個無雙表姐嗰個造型同埋演繹，所以喺《黃金花》嘅時候，會更好深刻同埋覺得好震撼。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：何永寧、Sapna<br />\n髮型：Euling Chow of IL COLPO TST<br />\n服裝提供：Sportmax、Nike<br />\n場地提供：FFG武術健身中心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【最佳女主角提名】<br />\n<br />\n周秀娜《29+1》<br />\n周迅《明月幾時有》<br />\n鄧麗欣《空手道》<br />\n張艾嘉《相愛相親》<br />\n毛舜筠《黃金花》<br />\n資料來源：金像獎大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180415/large/15ec6p15e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180415%2Flarge%2F15ec6p15e.jpg&h=d8325434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張艾嘉《相愛相親》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n娜姐攞獎死而無憾<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n毛舜筠了解對手<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n鄭中基若封帝感謝太太<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n凌文龍佛系爭獎<br />\n<br />\n娛樂名人 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚 2000-2330 第37屆香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮 ViuTV 99台 (4月15日 星期日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/629720/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/629720/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af6c94cf628acf15e761b1b04ef4c905f0cd302d","tid":629722,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"最佳女主角覺得周迅反而都有機喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd948d21c595a0786c5926ba18c1f812d2d54b5","tid":629722,"uid":5375,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"張艾嘉拍呢類野好似幾有心得 幾年前睇過念念唔差"},{"pid":"cf4cd62445a64ac6c1e2d0f56e8d628807b7a0d8","tid":629722,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:18:25.000Z","msg":"場地提供：FFG武術健身中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a240dd94073766140798efe6bc73d1e8127e89b","tid":629722,"uid":31918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"相愛相親冇得輸啦"},{"pid":"7665319c1344e728ad984131e4fce2fe9b7268b9","tid":629722,"uid":108756,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af6c94cf628acf15e761b1b04ef4c905f0cd302d","tid":629722,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"最佳女主角覺得周迅反而都有機喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"好老實我覺得周迅同張艾嘉絕對係有料攞得起呢啲獎項既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係都係支持本地演員啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73da84cc2d119f499d26d9e876b4af89e4c5c406","tid":629722,"uid":71283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af6c94cf628acf15e761b1b04ef4c905f0cd302d","tid":629722,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"最佳女主角覺得周迅反而都有機喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.g